Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}This is the first time I've worn such light and smooth clothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:12.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:32.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:41.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This concludes the report on Claudia McCunnen's conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:47.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She plotted my downfall and lured me into a trap using Zwei, the current Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and obtained Wisemel's position.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can hardly express my admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:59.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lizzy Garland has informed us that Claudia McCunnen's whereabouts are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It should be impossible for her to restore her position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It might be a far-fetched story, Scythe Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but the basic facts seem to match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:17.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At your suggestion,\Nthe Godou clan who assisted Claudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...should still be cooperated with, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:27.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's true that the cocaine heist one year ago was very painful for Inferno,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:34.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}however, the profit made on markets by the Godou clan is worth far more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you look at it sentimentally,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:42.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and seeing how he purged his relatives after knowing the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:46.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I recommend that you accept Mr. Shiga's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:51.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, that is definitely an interesting suggestion, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:55.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course, the Godou clan's profit margin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:59.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...will be cut back as penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:04.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:10.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mr. Shiga, for tempting your companions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:14.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I promise a cruel punishment for Claudia McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My deepest gratitude, Mr. McGwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:23.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We are still trying to locate Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.44,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The real problem is Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:35.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it doesn't pose a problem, Mr. McGwire, could Ein be given that assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The old and new Phantom confront.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you fine working under the Bloodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Romero was killed by Isaac!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:54.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Bloodies are being backed by a new and bigger organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday Inferno's age will come without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:03.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you that desperate to climb the ranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've even given up on taking revenge for your brother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will go to the place Romero failed to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe that is a worthy requiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to surrender here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come with me, Lizzy Garland!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need you by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:28.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I may be mafia, but I won't become a fiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is a moral code...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...that needs to be prioritized over loss and gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:39.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you promise to adhere to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...then fine, Clau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:47.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Acting ahead of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You stupid idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No good, we can't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:06.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Report to Lizzie this is a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, I found the car key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It sure is a gorgeous car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:18.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to ride the owner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sure enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.34,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think you pretty much understand what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Claudia, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be making excuses to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All I did was try to survive in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I rewarded you with all I had, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't plan on giving up just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can still turn the table, Reiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:19.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}if I have your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to leave L.A. and meet up with the organization's East Coast branch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:28.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but to be safe from Inferno's agents, Reiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your shield is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll wait for you at the 39th Drive Inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This time my life is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:40.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I could erase that scar any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I haven't forgiven you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the meaning of that scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Disgrace and decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein, although once my finest creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you were marred by him twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:29.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, far from perfect, you are nothing more than trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:34.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nonetheless, I have the trash heap called Ein with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:39.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's because I believe the time for resurrection will come someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Exact vengeance with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:51.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you do that and regain the light within you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will erase those scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will love you as my creation once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My gratitude, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can Ein beat Azuma Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:16.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If necessary, she will defeat Zwei at the cost of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:19.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She won't hesitate to throw her life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, so she is disposable?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After losing my creation called Ein,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:33.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my art will be even closer to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:40.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As my first creation she warrants commemoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:45.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I don't highly value memorials.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:51.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Still, there must be a better way than assigning mass numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:58.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes a sketch can be better than what was expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can't know beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The muse's twisted prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...astonishes both artist and audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will the final act be a tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:11.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:16.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To entrust the falling curtain to fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...should excite and thrill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:39.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Won't it be a problem for you to dispose of her, Lizzy Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't underestimate me, who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You and Claudia are old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:49.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You might not be able to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up, you damn prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:10.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone who looses track of time will be disliked,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is where everything began.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:32.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Zwei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}My name is not Zwei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:15.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What have I done until today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've always wanted to drive like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:36.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With unequaled speed, leaving everything behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:39.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One day you will even fly throughout the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That true freedom would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:46.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After coming this far, what do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have no goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just go as far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You sure are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday you will tire and stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When that happens and you lose your footing, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:04.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are things you shouldn't have left behind, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:12.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's ok, though. Some scenery can only be seen if we move at this speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to chase that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Won't you do anything before death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With you as my opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was ordered to fight and win a proper battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:21.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ascertain who is the strongest Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If so, I will keep you company until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:54.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even now, you are still given reasons to fight this viciously...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...by that Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:01.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't win this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}because I don't want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Killing you and escaping from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what would I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What would change?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:40.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Being deceived and manipulated,\Nunable to protect what's precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hate this repetition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let it end by your hands this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:53.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't condemn you, it's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't bear it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:04.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you still fight to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even now, you still fight for Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:09.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:18.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My life's meaning is... {\alpha&HFF&\t(2650,2700,\alpha&H00&)}this scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You told me to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I vowed to fight of my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a mark which you carved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I yearned for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it was a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the strength you showed that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:56.97,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and the oath you carved into my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:01.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...are the reasons I couldn't throw my life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are my other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As my substitute,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}walking the path I abandoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:14.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you fought and resisted while you moved ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I was able to live by seeing a dream of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:23.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}believing my other half to be living freely out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:28.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This scar has always reminded me of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:34.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I can't endure this pain forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:38.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you want to give up, nobody will blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:40.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you want to rip the seam of the oath we made that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...kill me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let everything end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:54.06,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:55.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am a failure for Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a doll waiting to be thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:03.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:08.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If this world isn't endless hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it's only because you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:24.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to be left in a world where you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:29.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't keep any of the promises I made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:31.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought I had lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.19,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:45.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But... If our promise has subsisted to this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I want to keep it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will take you away from Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fall of the curtain seems to have been disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:10.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe this is just another intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:20.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:11.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Thank you, Reiji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'll cherish it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:18.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I'll cherish it forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:19.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:27.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be coming to where you are for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still have things I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:32.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said you would never leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:43.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said we would be together.
